7. Joint guarantee and other securities
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN. reserves its right to realise any securities applied by you or
third party and write off the revenue at the option of
&BANKNAVN.. The third party guarantor has no right of recourse.
