8. Notification right and right to dividend upon your liquidation
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If the third party guarantor has to discharge your obligations towards
&BANKNAVN., &BANKNAVN. has notification right and right to dividend
of the amount paid in your estate.
