Specifically about guarantee
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
The following additional provisions apply for loans and credits secured by
guarantee.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
1. Extent of guarantee
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
The third party guarantor is held liable for your obligations towards
&BANKNAVN., including interest and other minor debt services, to
the extent that the total amount to be paid does not exceed the principal
amount of the loan or the credit limit on placing the guarantee.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
2. Expiry
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Guarantee  expires after 10 years, however, after 5 years in case of
guarantee of credit with floating loan amount and loans without fixed due
date. The claim of &BANKNAVN. against the third party guarantor does not
expire if the claim is sustained prior to the expiry of the guarantee.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
3. Reversal
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If the loan/credit is repaid, fully or partly, and the payment or
additional security is set aside at a later point in time, the guarantee
will be maintained, whether you or &BANKNAVN. has notified the third
party guarantor of the repayment or not.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
4. Use of payments
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Payments from third party guarantors are first of all used in settlement
of interest, commission and expenses, secondly in settlement of other debt
secured by the third party guarantor.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If the loan/credit is not fully secured by guarantee, your payments, or
payments from others than the third party guarantor, are first of all used
in settlement of the unsecured part of the debt.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
5. Respite
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Without consent of third party guarantor, &BANKNAVN. may grant a respite
as to payment of instalments, interest and other expenses, however, with
deference to article 48 of the Danish Financial Business Act.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
6. Voting right at creditors' meetings
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
At any creditors' meeting regarding you, &BANKNAVN. will
exercise the voting right connected to the object of the guarantee. This
applies until &BANKNAVN. has obtained full and irrefutable settlement of
its claims.
.sp 5mm
